title: On ED’s plea, HC nixes order to release some funds of finance firm to pay employees - The New Indian Express
content: On ED’s plea, HC nixes order to release some funds of finance firm to pay employees  The New Indian Express
description: Within a short span of time, the company made foreign outward remittances worth Rs 429.29 crore in the name of payments for non-existent software services received from related foreign companies.
